sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Data Scientist
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Webhook as Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Controller as Spark Operator Controller<br/>8080/metrics 8081/health
    participant SparkSubmit as spark-submit<br/>(local exec)
    participant Driver as Spark Driver Pod<br/>7078/TCP, 7079/TCP
    participant Executors as Spark Executor Pods
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 1: SparkApplication Submission and Execution

    User->>K8sAPI: POST SparkApplication CR<br/>HTTPS/6443, Bearer token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-.../sparkapplication<br/>HTTPS/9443, API server client cert
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admission Response (validated + defaulted)
    K8sAPI-->>User: CR Created

    K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch event: SparkApplication created
    Controller->>SparkSubmit: Invoke spark-submit binary<br/>(local process exec)
    SparkSubmit->>K8sAPI: Create Driver Pod<br/>HTTPS/6443, SA token

    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /mutate--v1-pod<br/>HTTPS/9443, API server client cert
    Note right of Webhook: 25+ mutations:<br/>env vars, volumes,<br/>ports, init containers,<br/>GPU, Prometheus agent,<br/>security context,<br/>scheduling, DNS

    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Mutated Pod spec

    Driver->>K8sAPI: Create Executor Pods<br/>HTTPS/6443, SA token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /mutate--v1-pod (executors)<br/>HTTPS/9443, API server client cert
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Mutated Executor Pod specs

    Driver->>Executors: Spark RPC<br/>7078/TCP, 7079/TCP (plaintext)
    Executors-->>Driver: Task results<br/>Block Manager 7079/TCP

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Update SparkApplication status<br/>HTTPS/6443, SA token

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 2: ScheduledSparkApplication

    Controller->>Controller: Cron trigger fires
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create child SparkApplication CR<br/>HTTPS/6443, SA token
    Note right of Controller: Follows Flow 1 steps above
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Enforce concurrency policy<br/>(Allow/Forbid/Replace)
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Clean up old runs (history limit)

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 3: Spark Connect Server

    User->>K8sAPI: POST SparkConnect CR<br/>HTTPS/6443, Bearer token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ConfigMap (executor template)<br/>HTTPS/6443, SA token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Server Pod + Service<br/>HTTPS/6443, SA token

    User->>Driver: gRPC/HTTP2 Connect<br/>15002/TCP (plaintext)
    Driver->>Executors: Spark RPC<br/>7078/TCP, 7079/TCP (plaintext)

    Note over User,Prometheus: Monitoring

    Prometheus->>Controller: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/8080 (unauthenticated)
    Controller-->>Prometheus: Prometheus metrics<br/>(app count, submit count,<br/>execution times, executor metrics)
